{
  "id": "RAW_5ecea269",
  "title": "智谱放大招！实测 GLM-4.6V，它也太会“看图做事”了",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIwMTU5OTQ1Nw==&mid=2653723230&idx=1&sn=3025584e9fa28757b92d0086a8d109ec",
  "date": "2025-12-08 12:30:00",
  "author": "(沃垠AI)",
  "siteName": "沃垠AI",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p>\n   <br>\n  </p>\n  <div style=\"padding:0px 6px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: 100%;height: auto;vertical-align: top;overflow-x: hidden;overflow-y: auto;scroll-snap-type: y mandatory;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"overflow: visible;height: 0px;padding-top: 0.02px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0.5em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"miw1dpnb1tuj\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-imgfileid=\"506239548\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"4.1481481\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;background-color: transparent;border-radius: 6px;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7ca2f4e8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FNX4HOlP6ibC9ib1no8x1rvWBuV6gQE8oqVMyvg2s8eVPFMicDYnvzMrz1OgQmpicg690lxpYkBkhmALsP4VouH7fog%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;text-align: right;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">这篇文章，由AI一键直出⬆️</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">今天，智谱发布并开源了</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">GLM-4.6V多模态模型</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">，一个是向云端服务的106B基础版，一个是面向本地部署的9B轻量版。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">模型下载：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><a href=\"https://huggingface.co/collections/zai-org/glm-46v\" target=\"_blank\">https://huggingface.co/collections/zai-org/glm-46v</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">API调用平台：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><a href=\"https://www.bigmodel.cn\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bigmodel.cn</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">MCP调用入口：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><a href=\"https://docs.bigmodel.cn/cn/coding-plan/mcp/vision-mcp-server\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.bigmodel.cn/cn/coding-plan/mcp/vision-mcp-server</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">开头这篇文章，便是由GLM-4.6V-106B直接生成。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">可以看到，GLM-4.6V除了在视觉理解上能够“看懂”多模态内容外，还具备工具调用能力（Function Call）能够直接做“执行”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">官方说，这是一个</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">原生具备多模态工具调用能力</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">的模型。比如，可以处理图文混排、识图购物、导购以及各种Agent场景的复杂视觉任务。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">省流：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">感知→理解→执行，都在一个推理链里完成，无需外部工程化。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 8px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"506236477\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.22833333333333333\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"600\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d2b71a2a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FNX4HOlP6ibCicV1QppcudDqHNibe1FiaSiaXvic8DcjbZP6CtUD7nHjdLA0fB0eibP1sbkJBqTVafECcdFc416I0ia2VHw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(210, 79, 240);font-weight: bold;\">一手实测</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">我知道，这么说，你可能还是没懂。下面，我们来看点实际的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">打开</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">Z.ai</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">，选择模型“GLM-4.6V”，根据任务需要选择合适的工具，开启“深度思考”，进行体验。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 16px;padding: 0.5em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"miw1dw2p1d2z\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-imgfileid=\"506239550\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.6842592592592592\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;background-color: transparent;border-radius: 6px;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7d9417bb&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FNX4HOlP6ibC9ib1no8x1rvWBuV6gQE8oqVQgm2jMbKvvfeAOm0ibm6RTOic68bW8fWYa7eksREZ3YMhNVibeAlPQG8A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这里，简单分享几点技巧：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">①建议所有场景都开启深度思考</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">，除非是明确的简单行为，比如OCR识别。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">②不需要把所有工具都勾选</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">，建议根据自己的任务情况来选择。比如coding任务，它不太需要图像处理、图像搜索和购物搜索，那就把4个工具都关掉。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">③</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">如果不知道自己需要什么样的工具，可以</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">点下方的胶囊入口</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 16px;padding: 0.5em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"miw1e1kq1ifq\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-imgfileid=\"506239549\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.45615982241953384\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"901\" style=\"box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;background-color: transparent;border-radius: 6px;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2600181a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FNX4HOlP6ibC9ib1no8x1rvWBuV6gQE8oqVs8sPWjLDdvbSLuZwicJnfft2gdHpGsyWpUfgjDrcnPibkqzOtrLsV6NA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">这里内置了6个场景：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">识图搜图、图文扫描、文档解读、视频理解、商品比价和数理解题。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: underline;\">1）复刻网页</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">我们先来复刻一个网页，比如复刻抖音电脑版。</span></span></p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\">请给我这个网页截图的HTML Code，如果网页包含图片素材，一定要给我图片，不要用Placeholder替代。</span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 16px;padding: 0.5em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"miw1e6zp14ry\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-imgfileid=\"506239551\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.6148148148148148\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;background-color: transparent;border-radius: 6px;box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2b47f656&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FNX4HOlP6ibC9ib1no8x1rvWBuV6gQE8oqVV8IgEJlfDXt0hplAYhcJVRFFWGoS0Z6fTKYQ3vqibYC2u56UsicVaLFA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这是成品，跟抖音网页版几乎一模一样。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;padding: 0.5em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"miw1ebm1169x\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-imgfileid=\"506239552\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.7101851851851851\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;background-color: transparent;border-radius: 6px;box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a902979d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FNX4HOlP6ibC9ib1no8x1rvWBuV6gQE8oqVUlS7ajNiaFsWBn2bnqnT0Hc2VLHMeH8aAhL1BYkNeDE2mXHkM94O6Qg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">复刻小红书。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0.5em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"miw1efyyiv5\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-imgfileid=\"506239553\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.8472222222222222\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;background-color: transparent;border-radius: 6px;box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2bbfc157&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FNX4HOlP6ibC9ib1no8x1rvWBuV6gQE8oqVqQot23k7JoDe4YaPiavtKBW3mQqVyo8X0cF8exfRGaKKQJqlSJfPuJA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">提示词：复刻这个网页。如果网页包含图片素材，请联网搜索与内容适配的图片进行替代，不要使用占位图。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">复刻OpenAI News。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0.5em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"miw1d0737v3\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-imgfileid=\"506239554\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.8648148148148148\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;background-color: transparent;border-radius: 6px;box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a74e738b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FNX4HOlP6ibC9ib1no8x1rvWBuV6gQE8oqVuD5xbGGRKFtYBxribckwH6TcT2t7wEvMCyUq0YmvPGicDaXsWxq3lC9w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">提示词：请给我这个网页截图的HTML Code，如果网页包含图片素材，一定要给我图片，不要用Placeholder替代。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">个人体验来看，GLM-4.6V的前端能力离Gemini 3 Pro还差了那么一点。但话又说回来，又有谁的前端能力能比得过Gemini 3呢？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">不同的是，GLM-4.6V的前端复刻支持多轮视觉交互修改，可以在生成的网页截图上框选区域进行修改，比如“把这个按钮向左移一点，颜色改为橘红色”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">案例来自官方视频</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: underline;\">2）文档解读+写作</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">之前，很多模型一直解决不了的图文同时输出能力，GLM-4.6V这次做到了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">比如，我们拿一份Transformer论文给它，然后输入提示词：</span></span></p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\">根据附件论文，写一篇图文并茂的微信公众号文章来介绍这篇论文，语言要通俗易懂、生动有趣，尽量让小学生也能听懂。使用图文并茂的markdown格式输出。</span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">然后，就得到了一篇图文并茂的公众号文章。</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"padding:0px 6px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;