ght: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这是来自</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(210, 79, 240);font-weight: bold;\">沃垠AI</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">群里的一张图片，用户用NBP生成的，拿来上课非常好使。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 16px;padding: 0.5em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"miw1i3wqm8z\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-imgfileid=\"506239578\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5574074074074075\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;background-color: transparent;border-radius: 6px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=26bf312c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FNX4HOlP6ibC9ib1no8x1rvWBuV6gQE8oqVmcMspibRNKc6QUtbBPILBlDtlLerHDfzxs5eZg0BEzfulPMJ1gHb3XA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">我试着用GLM-4.6V反推了一下提示词。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 16px;padding: 0.5em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"miw1i7byuer\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-imgfileid=\"506239579\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.7882472137791287\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"987\" style=\"box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;background-color: transparent;border-radius: 6px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1b175630&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FNX4HOlP6ibC9ib1no8x1rvWBuV6gQE8oqVsQHwD1PRN7DbhINCiciabiadgk6qS7dRnicNzDnFJQ1bmJLZRStTOBlUfw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">得到提示词：</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"font-weight:400;font-size:15px;line-height:1;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div style=\"border:1px solid rgb(242, 235, 235);border-radius:5px;padding:10px;overflow:hidden;display:inline-block;width:100%;margin-top:10px;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:10px;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"font-size: 14px;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Traditional Chinese ink - wash style educational infographic titled \"Water Journey: Chinese Vocabulary Memory Aid\", illustrating the water radical (氵) through nature. Features a flowing river (江, Jiāng - River), river (河, Hé - River), lake (湖, Hú - Lake), ocean (海, Hǎi - Ocean), and swim (泳, Yǒng - Swim) with Chinese characters, pinyin, and English translations. Includes mountains, pine trees, waterfalls, clouds, small boats, and swimmers. Soft pastel color palette with beige background, blue water, earthy mountain tones. Composition shows water flow from river to lake to ocean, with arrows indicating direction. Detailed landscape with traditional Chinese artistic elements, suitable for language learning.</span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">中文：传统中国水墨风格教育信息图，标题为“Water Journey: Chinese Vocabulary Memory Aid”（《水之旅：中文词汇记忆辅助》），通过自然展示水部首（氵）。画面包含流动的江（江，Jiāng - River）、河（河，Hé - River）、湖（湖，Hú - Lake）、海（海，Hǎi - Ocean）和游泳（泳，Yǒng - Swim），配有汉字、拼音和英文翻译。包含山脉、松树、瀑布、云朵、小船和游泳者。柔和的 pastel 色彩，米色背景，蓝色水域，土色调的山脉。构图展示水流从河流到湖泊再到海洋，箭头指示方向。细节丰富的景观，具有传统中国艺术元素，适合语言学习。</span></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">发到即梦上，没想到直接就生成了类似的图。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;padding: 0.5em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"miw1id171h8f\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-imgfileid=\"506239580\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.3435700575815739\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1042\" style=\"box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;background-color: transparent;border-radius: 6px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b34864dd&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FNX4HOlP6ibC9ib1no8x1rvWBuV6gQE8oqVseeKL77cSsgn40XHMlwunvribVNuxnS0dMlU1NeywBH8cb0tZxeFNBQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">以后，用GLM-4.6V做反推真的太容易了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: underline;\">7）视频理解</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">我把GLM-4.6V官方介绍视频里的多个功能，用3倍速剪在了一块。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">发给GLM-4.6V问：这支视频讲了什么？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 16px;padding: 0.5em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"miw1ihqu1e52\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-imgfileid=\"506239581\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"2.1431451612903225\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"992\" style=\"box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;background-color: transparent;border-radius: 6px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e9a61c0f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FNX4HOlP6ibC9ib1no8x1rvWBuV6gQE8oqVa0o22cM2g1DnWsVjxNr3V4zbNeC31jK0Utt6haVQeSibYE6GDCgS1Dg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">GLM-4.6V的回答还是挺准的，而且精确定位到了帧数。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"506236476\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.20666666666666667\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"600\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=616247c5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FNX4HOlP6ibCicV1QppcudDqHNibe1FiaSiaXvchrPAK3S9ibJjY6ibrzfXP6eUeh1IhG5DzGiaatTn9k3XGl1vebRJm43Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(210, 79, 240);font-weight: bold;\">写在最后</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">从个人实测来看，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">GML-4.6V的工具调用能力</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">（Function Call）</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">非常出色</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">，而且是原生就支持。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">做到了「图像即参数，结果即上下文」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">虽然在一些能力上（比如写作、前端）还达不到顶尖，这需要更强力的基模，但这一手工具调用能力就已经是很多VLM不能比的了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">所以，这是一个</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">天然适合做Agentic基座的模型</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">，可以为真实业务场景赋能。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">自GLM-4.6以来，我们看到，智谱正在开发者生态爆发相当大的潜力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">今天，又一个强力VLM模型来袭，而且</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">已经加入智谱Coding Plan</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><img style=\"display:inline-block;width:20px;vertical-align:middle;background-size:cover;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-w=\"20\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=525a59a7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fres.wx.qq.com%2Ft%2Fwx_fed%2Fwe-emoji%2Fres%2Fassets%2Fnewemoji%2FWatermelon.png\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">而这，只是智谱开源周的Day 1。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-indent: 0px;margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">说实话，有点期待接下来的几天了。</span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文深度实测了智谱新发布的 GLM-4.6V 多模态模型，展示其原生多模态工具调用能力，尤其在视觉理解和执行方面的出色表现，并提供丰富的应用案例。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文深度实测了智谱新发布的 GLM-4.6V 多模态模型，展示其原生多模态工具调用能力，尤其在视觉理解和执行方面的出色表现，并提供丰富的应用案例。",
  "summary": "文章详细评测了智谱新发布的 GLM-4.6V 多模态模型，包括云端 106B 基础版和本地 9B 轻量版。该模型核心亮点是其原生的多模态工具调用能力（Function Call），实现了感知、理解、执行在同一推理链中完成，无需外部工程化。文章通过复刻网页、文档解读与写作、商品比价、识别疑难文字、地图推理和图片反推等七个具体案例，全面展示了 GLM-4.6V 在复杂视觉任务处理上的强大能力。尤其在文档图文混合内容理解和图片内容识别方面表现突出，提升了内容创作和信息获取效率。文章也指出了其在前端复刻能力上与顶尖模型仍有差距，但强调了其作为 Agentic 基座模型的巨大潜力。",
